headline: Wellness Real Estate Market Outlook Report to 2030: Key Vendor Profiles for Brookfield Asset Management, CBRE Group, China Vanke, Delos Living, and Skanska
summary: The Wellness Real Estate Market, valued at USD 463.24 billion in 2024, is projected to double, reaching USD 944.11 billion by 2030, with a CAGR of 12.60%. The physical wellness segment leads with over 43% market share. Mixed-use developments exhibit the highest growth at 13.28%. Urban areas and new developments dominate the market, while North America holds a 40%+ share, and the Middle East & Africa record the fastest growth, 14.62%.
